{"tid":2294068,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當日中大之役班退休人形生物消失哂","createTime":"2020-11-20T17:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T17:45:48.000Z","uid":66324,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9e968c9ed874d0695b6f38e3e3596fa831ce6957","tid":2294068,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T17:16:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BC%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E8%99%95%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2596%25BC%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%2589%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E4%25BA%258B%2F&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM30xj1a1M9JfR6d2dSWReNkw%3D&h=14945363\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2596%25BC%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%2589%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E4%25BA%258B%2F&h=fefae4a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BC%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E8%99%95%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n我有三件關於中大保安處的事情想分享。<br />\n<br />\n1. 去年 11 月 11 日至 12 日，在 12 晚大規模衝突之前，老師們都在想辦法讓事態降溫。當時的想法，是讓警察退到二橋的另一邊，校園的這一邊就由中大保安負責，這樣學生就不會在環迴路見到警察，二橋上面也不會有人，變成中立的緩衝地帶。一開始提這方案時，校方不太積極，<span class=\"red\">我們發現原來當時校方根本叫不動保安處，他們好像是在曠工一樣</span>。於是，我們自發提議由老師做人盾去守二橋。到了校長落二橋談判，護送校長到現場的是老師，開路保護校長在催淚煙霧中離開的也是老師，<span class=\"red\">保安處全日失蹤</span>。<br />\n<br />\n2. 到了 11 月 15 日，示威者撤離二橋。當時老師們認為校方必須立即派人到現場，宣示校方已重新控制局面，以免再發事端。<span class=\"red\">不過，保安處繼續失蹤</span>。第一批在示威者撤離二橋後到達現場的校方成員，仍然是老師代表。<br />\n<br />\n3. 一年後，因為接受媒體訪問，我又再回到二橋附近。現在保安處在二橋已有更亭，每次到場他們都會過來查問。我說我是新聞院的老師，他們還會客氣一點；如果我不說話，他們對著學生，就會叫他們離開，說他們聚集在二橋會「危險」。我想，你們遲到一整年了，最危險的時候你們都不在，現在反過來和我說危險？"},{"pid":"e7a449e2ff0c77c0429b55693c634da1f394521c","tid":2294068,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T17:20:59.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"9dfe7b87ebf2758af989865f2f44197ad99965b4","tid":2294068,"uid":7854,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T17:22:59.000Z","msg":"前排成班藍屍衝入大學撕牆都係無影啦<br />\n<br />\n隔兩日記者入去採訪就露番個龜頭出黎"},{"pid":"77955700c920d2bbdd00834183603ce876f49f8f","tid":2294068,"uid":66324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9dfe7b87ebf2758af989865f2f44197ad99965b4","tid":2294068,"uid":7854,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T17:22:59.000Z","msg":"前排成班藍屍衝入大學撕牆都係無影啦<br />\n<br />\n隔兩日記者入去採訪就露番個龜頭出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T17:25:26.000Z","msg":"保安即係退休人形生物 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c241cbc8dce4970d94a6dd409a57652d7cc49f","tid":2294068,"uid":79410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T17:26:44.000Z","msg":"所有大學既保安. 都已經直屬黑警 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a576415ce939935a586009aaa3c3c6ac1b107f8","tid":2294068,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T17:30:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bf27aa3316409f5efb4156a702352e513d0aa2d4","tid":2294068,"uid":66324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"24c241cbc8dce4970d94a6dd409a57652d7cc49f","tid":2294068,"uid":79410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T17:26:44.000Z","msg":"所有大學既保安. 都已經直屬黑警 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T17:32:38.000Z","msg":"保安公司的高層係咩人? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b830b0e87ba469831bde636ee8cd1b4e10d116ff","tid":2294068,"uid":337608,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T17:34:11.000Z","msg":"唔